summary: AN ORDINANCE changing the manner of licensing tradeshows and street fairs and similar events, imposing duties upon the organizer, replacing individual business fees for each participant with a variable fee for the entire event, providing for a civil penalty, and amending Seattle Municipal Code Sections 6.20.010 and 5.44.130, and adding new sections 6.20.015, -.020, -.030, -.040, -.050, -.060, -.070, and -.100 in connection therewith.
